  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389130/extras/d0c3dc6dcdfcb7834e41d09b26a513c3.poster.avif?t=1607613960\" width=600 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389130/extras/d0c3dc6dcdfcb7834e41d09b26a513c3.webm?t=1607613960\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>In this adventure game, you need your math skills to survive and protect the tourists. Don't let the forest creatures get near them!<br><strong>Folkloric Excursion</strong> let you practice the basic four operations while you gather information about brazilian folklore's creatures. Try to survive longer and to provide a great excursion for all excursionists that are traveling in this journey with you.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Solve operations and acquire a lot of points!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389130/extras/d42993eb268ecb11dd8f9c0191acf4ad.webp?t=1607613960\" width=34 height=27 /></span><br></li><li>Defeat enemies to gather informations to fill the bestiary!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389130/extras/a26ec538ae23c01aab41139a19d33044.webp?t=1607613960\" width=36 height=27 /></span><br></li><li>Pick up coins to buy skins in the shop!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389130/extras/441a298a10bc65fef1cc82b222c20227.webp?t=1607613960\" width=38 height=18 /></span><br></li><li>Level up to be able to use powerful skills against your enemies!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389130/extras/d0eaa84a43ceb255ecd4569c173bcb86.webp?t=1607613960\" width=61 height=25 /></span><br></li><li>Be careful, enemies are more dangerous at night!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389130/extras/c0a164ddcf84f7657e54b93e48a9e1c6.webp?t=1607613960\" width=26 height=26 /></span><br></li><li>Reach the top of the leaderboard!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389130/extras/7c8989470e6f08792785613910a4c08a.webp?t=1607613960\" width=29 height=30 /></span></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389130/extras/d0c3dc6dcdfcb7834e41d09b26a513c3.poster.avif?t=1607613960\" width=600 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389130/extras/d0c3dc6dcdfcb7834e41d09b26a513c3.webm?t=1607613960\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>In this adventure game, you need your math skills to survive and protect the tourists. Don't let the forest creatures get near them!<br><strong>Folkloric Excursion</strong> let you practice the basic four operations while you gather information about brazilian folklore's creatures. Try to survive longer and to provide a great excursion for all excursionists that are traveling in this journey with you.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Solve operations and acquire a lot of points!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389130/extras/d42993eb268ecb11dd8f9c0191acf4ad.webp?t=1607613960\" width=34 height=27 /></span><br></li><li>Defeat enemies to gather informations to fill the bestiary!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389130/extras/a26ec538ae23c01aab41139a19d33044.webp?t=1607613960\" width=36 height=27 /></span><br></li><li>Pick up coins to buy skins in the shop!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389130/extras/441a298a10bc65fef1cc82b222c20227.webp?t=1607613960\" width=38 height=18 /></span><br></li><li>Level up to be able to use powerful skills against your enemies!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389130/extras/d0eaa84a43ceb255ecd4569c173bcb86.webp?t=1607613960\" width=61 height=25 /></span><br></li><li>Be careful, enemies are more dangerous at night!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389130/extras/c0a164ddcf84f7657e54b93e48a9e1c6.webp?t=1607613960\" width=26 height=26 /></span><br></li><li>Reach the top of the leaderboard!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389130/extras/7c8989470e6f08792785613910a4c08a.webp?t=1607613960\" width=29 height=30 /></span></li></ul>",
